#mars #milankovitchcycle #earth 

0:00 Milankovitch cycles study 
2:00 How these cycles work: eccentricity 
3:00 Obliquity 
3:40 Axial Precession 
4:30 Additional mechanisms 
5:30 Volcanic effects!
title: Bizarre Connection Between Milankovitch Cycles, Mars and Volcanoes
